"title": "8739: evil, examples of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8739",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Biblical examples of evil are many and varied.</p>\n<h2>Evil disasters sent by God in judgment</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:20\">GEN 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24\">GEN 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:20\">EXO 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:6\">EXO 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:17\">EXO 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:24\">EXO 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:6\">EXO 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:10\">EXO 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:23\">EXO 9:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:13\">EXO 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:22\">EXO 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:29\">EXO 12:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:21-Num16:22\">NUM 16:21–16:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:6\">1SA 5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:15\">2SA 24:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1\">1KI 17:1</a></p>\n<h2>Other disasters</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">GEN 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1\">GEN 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:54\">GEN 41:54</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:1\">AMO 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:4\">LUK 13:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28\">ACT 11:28</a></p>\n<h2>National evil</h2>\n<h3>Israel guilty of evil</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:7\">EXO 32:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:11\">NUM 14:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:5\">DEU 32:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:11-Judg2:15\">JDG 2:11–2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:7\">JDG 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:1\">JDG 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:1\">JDG 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:6\">JDG 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:1\">JDG 13:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:28\">NEH 9:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:12\">ISA 65:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:4-Amos2:8\">AMO 2:4–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Threats to Israel from other nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:1\">JDG 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:7\">1SA 7:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:10-2Chr20:11\">2CH 20:10–20:11</a></p>\n<h3>Judgment on other nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:2\">1SA 15:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:29-Isa14:30\">ISA 14:29–14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:1\">ISA 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:1\">ISA 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:1\">ISA 19:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:10\">JER 46:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:25-Jer46:26\">JER 46:25–46:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer47:4\">JER 47:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:1\">JER 48:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:1-Jer49:2\">JER 49:1–49:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:7-Jer49:8\">JER 49:7–49:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:35-Jer49:38\">JER 49:35–49:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:1-Jer50:2\">JER 50:1–50:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:11\">AMO 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:13\">AMO 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:1\">AMO 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>Evil rulers</h2>\n<h3>Of Israel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:31\">1KI 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:25-1Kgs15:26\">1KI 15:25–15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:33-1Kgs15:34\">1KI 15:33–15:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:12-1Kgs16:13\">1KI 16:12–16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:18-1Kgs16:19\">1KI 16:18–16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:30\">1KI 16:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:25\">1KI 21:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:51-1Kgs22:52\">1KI 22:51–22:52</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:31\">2KI 10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:1-2Kgs13:2\">2KI 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:10-2Kgs13:11\">2KI 13:10–13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:23-2Kgs14:24\">2KI 14:23–14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:8-2Kgs15:9\">2KI 15:8–15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:17-2Kgs15:18\">2KI 15:17–15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:24\">2KI 15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:27-2Kgs15:28\">2KI 15:27–15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:1-2Kgs17:2\">2KI 17:1–17:2</a></p>\n<h3>Of Judah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:4\">1KI 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:1-1Kgs15:3\">1KI 15:1–15:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:16-2Kgs8:18\">2KI 8:16–8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:26-2Kgs8:27\">2KI 8:26–8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:1\">2KI 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:2\">2KI 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:1-2Kgs21:2\">2KI 21:1–21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:9\">2KI 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:19-2Kgs21:20\">2KI 21:19–21:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:31-2Kgs23:32\">2KI 23:31–23:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:36-2Kgs23:37\">2KI 23:36–23:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:8-2Kgs24:9\">2KI 24:8–24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:18-2Kgs24:19\">2KI 24:18–24:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:13-2Chr12:14\">2CH 12:13–12:14</a></p>\n<h3>Of other nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:2\">EXO 5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:23\">NUM 21:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:1-Judg4:3\">JDG 4:1–4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:13\">2KI 18:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:3-Isa14:6\">ISA 14:3–14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:13-Isa14:14\">ISA 14:13–14:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:31\">DAN 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22\">DAN 5:22</a></p>\n<h2>Evil religious leaders</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:12\">1SA 2:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:19\">1KI 18:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:11\">JER 23:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:4\">EZK 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:2\">EZK 34:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:1\">HOS 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:6\">MIC 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:4\">ZEP 3:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:15\">MAT 23:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14\">REV 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Opponents of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:16\">MAT 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:14\">MAT 12:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:6\">MRK 3:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:28\">LUK 4:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:18\">JHN 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:12\">JHN 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:32\">JHN 7:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:59\">JHN 8:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:20\">JHN 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:31\">JHN 10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:6\">JHN 19:6</a></p>\n<h2>Opponents of the church</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:3\">ACT 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:18\">ACT 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:9\">ACT 6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1-Acts8:3\">ACT 8:1–8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:1\">ACT 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:8\">ACT 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:50\">ACT 13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:5\">ACT 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19\">ACT 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19\">ACT 16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:5\">ACT 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:13\">ACT 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12\">ACT 18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:29\">ACT 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:3\">ACT 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:27\">ACT 21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:12\">ACT 23:12</a></p>\n<h2>Evil influences</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:1\">NUM 25:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:16\">NUM 31:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:9\">DEU 18:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:9\">HOS 7:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:6\">1CO 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:10\">1CO 8:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:26\">1JN 2:26</a></p>",
